<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      }
      .success-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #10b981;
        color: white;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ§ª QA Lab SMTP Test</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="success-badge">âœ… SMTP Connection Successful</div>
      
      <h2>Hello!</h2>
      
      <p>This is a test email from your QA Lab system administration panel.</p>
      
      <p><strong>Test Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Recipient:</strong> <%= @email %></li>
        <li><strong>Sent at:</strong> <%= @timestamp %></li>
        <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> SMTP Configuration Test</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>If you're receiving this email, it means your SMTP settings are configured correctly and QA Lab can successfully send emails!</p>
      
      <p><strong>What this confirms:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>SMTP server connection is working</li>
        <li>Authentication credentials are valid</li>
        <li>Email delivery is functioning</li>
        <li>From/Reply-to addresses are properly configured</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>You can now be confident that QA Lab will be able to send notifications, invitations, and other important emails to your users.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was automatically generated by QA Lab System Administration</p>
      <p>If you did not request this test, please contact your system administrator</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>